soda /ˈsəʊdə/

(sodas) 

1. N-MASS Soda is a sweet carbonated drink. 汽水 [美国英语] 

例： ...a glass of diet soda. …一杯低热量汽水。 

2. N-COUNT A soda is a bottle of soda. 一瓶汽水 

例： They had liquor for the adults and sodas for the children. 他们为成年人准备了酒，为孩子们准备了汽水。 

3. N-UNCOUNT Soda is the same as . 苏打水 

4.  →  see also baking soda , club soda

